{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"root","type":"group","x":-100,"y":-3500,"width":2400,"height":7500,"label":"SLeads 系统完整架构与处理流程 (2026-03-12)"},
		
		{"id":"section1","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-3350,"width":2300,"height":950,"label":"一、数据收集层 (Data Collection)"},
		{"id":"s1_search","type":"text","text":"【搜索模式】PubMedSearchCollector\n\n实现原理：\n1. 接收关键词列表\n2. 构建搜索查询：'kw1' OR 'kw2' OR 'kw3'\n3. 调用 Jina Search API (s.jina.ai)\n4. 解析搜索结果，提取 URL\n5. 过滤只保留 pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov 域名\n6. 返回 URL 列表\n\n输入：\nkeywords = ['Multiplex Immunofluorescence', 'mIF', 'immunofluorescence']\n\n输出：\n['https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37105494/', ...]\n\n限制：\n- max_results 控制返回数量\n- Jina Search API 限制结果数","x":-30,"y":-3300,"width":550,"height":700},
		{"id":"s1_library","type":"text","text":"【库模式】SingleCellPapersCollector\n\n实现原理：\n1. 访问论文库 URL\n2. 使用 Jina Reader 读取页面\n3. 正则提取分页信息：'当前共找到 123 篇文献'\n4. 计算总页数\n5. 翻页读取（并发控制）\n6. 每页提取所有论文 URL\n7. 去重后返回\n\n输入：\nlibrary_url = 'https://single-cell-papers.bioinfo-assist.com'\nkeyword = 'mIF'\n\n输出：\n['https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37105494/', ...]\n\n正则模式：\n- https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/\\d+/\n- https://doi.org/10.\\d+/.*","x":550,"y":-3300,"width":550,"height":700},
		{"id":"s1_multi","type":"text","text":"【多模式合并】MultiModeCollector\n\n实现原理：\n1. 并发启动 Search 和 Library\n2. 分别收集 URL\n3. 合并结果到字典：{'search': [...], 'library': [...]}\n4. 调用 URLDeduplicator.merge_sources()\n5. 返回去重后的 URL 列表\n\n输出格式：\n[\n  {\n    'url': 'https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37105494/',\n    'sources': ['search', 'library']\n  },\n  ...\n]\n\n并发控制：\n- 两种模式并发执行\n- 各自的错误不影响对方","x":1130,"y":-3300,"width":550,"height":700},
		{"id":"s1_dedup","type":"text","text":"【URL去重】URLDeduplicator\n\n去重逻辑：\n1. 提取 PMID：/pubmed/\\d+/\n2. 提取 DOI：/doi.org/10.\\d+/.*\n3. URL 标准化：小写，去除尾部斜杠\n4. 优先级：PMID > DOI > URL\n5. 维护三个集合：seen_pmids, seen_dois, seen_urls\n6. 合并多源结果\n\n处理示例：\n输入：4 个 URL（含重复）\n输出：2 个唯一 URL\n\n状态统计：\n- seen_urls: 2\n- seen_pmids: 2\n- seen_dois: 0","x":1710,"y":-3300,"width":500,"height":700},
		
		{"id":"section2","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-2300,"width":2300,"height":1150,"label":"二、内容获取层 (Content Fetching)"},
		{"id":"s2_jina","type":"text","text":"【主力】JinaReaderClient\n\nAPI: r.jina.ai/{url}\n\n处理流程：\n1. 接收 URL\n2. 构建请求：https://r.jina.ai/{url}\n3. 发送 GET 请求\n4. 接收 Markdown 格式内容\n5. 提取纯文本\n6. 返回结果\n\n输入：\nurl = 'https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37105494/'\n\n输出：\n{\n  'success': True,\n  'content': 'Article Title: ...\\nAbstract: ...',\n  'source': 'jina'\n}\n\n特性：\n- 自动清理广告、导航\n- 保留结构化内容\n- 10秒超时","x":-30,"y":-2250,"width":700,"height":900},
		{"id":"s2_playwright","type":"text","text":"【兜底】PlaywrightClient\n\n触发条件：\n1. Jina Reader 失败\n2. 检测到反爬页面\n   - 'just a moment'\n   - 'cloudflare'\n   - 'checking your browser'\n\n处理流程：\n1. 启动无头浏览器\n2. 加载页面，等待渲染\n3. 等待反爬验证完成\n4. 提取页面文本\n5. 返回结果\n\n输入：\nurl = 'https://ccgp.gov.cn/...'\n\n输出：\n{\n  'success': True,\n  'content': '招标公告内容...',\n  'source': 'playwright'\n}\n\n特性：\n- 完整 JS 渲染\n- 30秒超时\n- 自动检测验证码","x":700,"y":-2250,"width":700,"height":900},
		{"id":"s2_fetcher","type":"text","text":"【统一接口】ContentFetcher\n\n工作流程：\n1. 接收 URL\n2. 优先调用 JinaReaderClient\n3. 判断是否成功：\n   - success=True: 返回结果\n   - success=False: 继续\n4. 检测反爬特征\n5. 调用 PlaywrightClient\n6. 返回最终结果\n7. 更新统计信息\n\n统计字段：\n- total_requests: 总请求数\n- jina_success: Jina 成功数\n- playwright_success: Playwright 成功数\n- success_rate: 成功率\n\n配置：\nenable_playwright=True 启用兜底","x":1430,"y":-2250,"width":780,"height":900},
		
		{"id":"section3","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-1050,"width":2300,"height":1400,"label":"三、LLM提取层 (LLM Extraction)"},
		{"id":"s3_rate","type":"text","text":"【速率控制】RateLimiter\n\n时间判断：\n- 高峰期 (14:00-18:00): 30秒/请求\n- 非高峰期: 20秒/请求\n\n工作流程：\n1. 请求前检查上次请求时间\n2. 计算需要等待的时间\n3. 如果未到等待时间，sleep\n4. 记录本次请求时间\n5. 返回允许继续\n\n429 重试逻辑：\n1. 检测 429 状态码\n2. 从响应头提取 Retry-After\n3. 等待指定秒数\n4. 重新发送请求\n5. 最多重试 3 次\n\n实现：\nasync with rate_limiter:\n    await call_llm()","x":-30,"y":-1000,"width":700,"height":950},
		{"id":"s3_extractor","type":"text","text":"【字段提取】LLMExtractor\n\nPrompt 模板：\n从以下论文内容中提取信息，以JSON格式返回：\n\n字段：\n- title: 文章标题\n- pmid: PubMed ID\n- doi: DOI\n- published_at: 发表时间 (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- corresponding_author:\n  - name: 通讯作者姓名\n  - affiliation: 单位\n  - email: 邮箱\n\n示例内容：\n{content}\n\n返回格式：\n{\"title\": \"...\", \"pmid\": \"...\"}\n\nGLM-5 配置：\n- API: open.bigmodel.cn\n- Model: glm-5\n- Temperature: 0.3\n- Max Tokens: 2000","x":700,"y":-1000,"width":700,"height":950},
		{"id":"s3_process","type":"text","text":"【提取处理流程】\n\n1. 调用 RateLimiter.acquire()\n   - 等待速率控制\n\n2. 发送请求到 GLM-5\n   - headers: Authorization: Bearer {token}\n   - body: {model, messages, temperature}\n\n3. 接收响应\n   - 解析 JSON\n   - 提取 content\n\n4. 验证 JSON 格式\n   - 尝试 json.loads()\n   - 失败：记录错误，返回 None\n\n5. 验证必填字段\n   - title: 必需\n   - pmid 或 doi: 至少一个\n\n6. 返回结构化数据\n\n异常处理：\n- JSON 解析失败 → 记录日志\n- 字段缺失 → 记录警告\n- API 错误 → 重试","x":1430,"y":-1000,"width":780,"height":950},
		
		{"id":"section4","type":"group","x":-50,"y":450,"width":2300,"height":1250,"label":"四、评分系统 (Scoring System)"},
		{"id":"s4_paper","type":"text","text":"【论文评分】PaperScorer\n\n输入：\nlead = {\n  'title': '...',\n  'institution': '...',\n  'email': '...',\n  'published_at': '2024-01-01'\n}\n\n评分维度（总分100）：\n\nA. 信息完备度 (20分)\n- 手机+邮箱+地址: 20\n- 缺手机号: 12\n- org_only: 5\n\nC. 决策链条完整度 (15分)\n- PI/联系人/设备科完整: 15\n- 仅联系人: 9\n- 仅单位: 3\n\nD. 匹配度 (25分)\n- 核心关键词+关联设备: 25\n- 泛关键词: 15\n- 弱匹配: 5\n\nE. 时效性 (20分)\n- 最近90天: 20\n- 90-180天: 12\n- 更早: 5\n\nG. 机构类型 (10分)\n- 985/211/科研院所: 10\n- 三甲医院: 7\n- 企业/其他: 4","x":-30,"y":500,"width":550,"height":1050},
		{"id":"s4_grade","type":"text","text":"【等级计算】\n\n分数 → 等级映射：\n- A >= 80\n- B = 65-79\n- C = 50-64\n- D < 50\n\n示例计算：\n\n论文: \"Multiplex IF...\"\n- 信息完备度: 12 (有邮箱，无手机)\n- 决策链条: 9 (仅联系人)\n- 匹配度: 25 (核心关键词)\n- 时效性: 20 (最近90天)\n- 机构类型: 7 (三甲医院)\n- 总分: 73\n- 等级: B\n\n保留数值分用于排序\n等级用于展示和筛选","x":550,"y":500,"width":550,"height":650},
		{"id":"s4_tender","type":"text","text":"【招标评分】TenderScorer\n\n输入：\nlead = {\n  'project_name': '...',\n  'institution': '...',\n  'budget': '100万',\n  'published_at': '2024-01-01'\n}\n\n评分维度（总分100）：\n\nA. 信息完备度 (15分)\n- 手机+邮箱+地址: 15\n- 缺手机号: 9\n- org_only: 4\n\nB. 预算状态 (20分)\n- 已明确预算/立项: 20\n- 有预算线索: 12\n- 经费不详: 5\n\nC. 决策链条完整度 (10分)\n- 完整: 10\n- 部分完整: 6\n- 仅单位: 2\n\nD. 匹配度 (20分)\n- 核心关键词: 20\n- 泛关键词: 12\n- 弱匹配: 4\n\nE. 时效性 (20分)\n- 最近90天: 20\n- 90-180天: 12\n- 更早: 5\n\nG. 机构类型 (10分)\n- 同论文评分\n\nF. 历史互动 (5分)\n- 已成交: 5\n- 已联系: 3\n- 无互动: 2","x":1130,"y":500,"width":550,"height":1050},
		{"id":"s4_keywords","type":"text","text":"【关键词匹配】\n\n核心关键词（100%）：\n- Multiplex Immunofluorescence\n- mIF\n- Tyramide Signal Amplification\n- TSA\n- Cyclic Immunofluorescence\n\n关联设备关键词（80%）：\n- Confocal Microscopy\n- 共聚焦显微镜\n- Olympus/ZEISS/Nikon/Leica\n\n泛关键词（60%）：\n- Immunofluorescence\n- 免疫荧光\n- Tissue Imaging\n\n弱匹配（20%）：\n- Fluorescence\n- Microscopy\n\n匹配逻辑：\n1. 检查标题和摘要\n2. 找到最高优先级关键词\n3. 返回对应分数","x":1710,"y":500,"width":500,"height":700},
		
		{"id":"section5","type":"group","x":-50,"y":1800,"width":2300,"height":950,"label":"五、数据存储层 (Database)"},
		{"id":"s5_schema","type":"text","text":"【数据库模型】PostgreSQL\n\nTable: paper_leads\n-------------------\nid (PK)\nsource_url (UNIQUE)\npmid (UNIQUE)\ndoi (UNIQUE)\ntitle\npublished_at\nname (通讯作者)\ninstitution\naddress\nemail\nphone\nall_authors (JSON)\nkeywords_matched (ARRAY)\nscore\ngrade (A/B/C/D)\nfeedback_status\nstrategy_version\nis_archived\ncreated_at\nupdated_at\n\nTable: crawled_urls\n-------------------\nurl (PK)\nsource_type\ncrawled_at\nstatus","x":-30,"y":1850,"width":700,"height":750},
		{"id":"s5_flow","type":"text","text":"【入库流程】\n\n1. 检查 URL 是否已爬取\n   SELECT * FROM crawled_urls\n   WHERE url = '{url}'\n   \n   - 存在 → 跳过\n   - 不存在 → 继续\n\n2. 插入 crawled_urls\n   INSERT INTO crawled_urls\n   (url, source_type, crawled_at, status)\n   VALUES ('{url}', 'paper', NOW(), 'success')\n\n3. 检查 PMID 是否存在\n   SELECT * FROM paper_leads\n   WHERE pmid = '{pmid}'\n   \n   - 存在 → 更新记录\n   - 不存在 → 插入新记录\n\n4. 插入/更新 paper_leads\n   INSERT INTO paper_leads (...) VALUES (...)\n   ON CONFLICT (pmid) DO UPDATE SET ...\n\n异常处理：\n- IntegrityError → 重复键，跳过\n- 其他错误 → 记录日志","x":700,"y":1850,"width":700,"height":750},
		{"id":"s5_query","type":"text","text":"【查询示例】\n\n1. 获取今日新增线索\nSELECT * FROM paper_leads\nWHERE DATE(created_at) = CURRENT_DATE\nORDER BY score DESC\n\n2. 获取高优线索 (A/B级)\nSELECT * FROM paper_leads\nWHERE grade IN ('A', 'B')\nAND is_archived = FALSE\nORDER BY score DESC\n\n3. 按机构统计\nSELECT institution, COUNT(*)\nFROM paper_leads\nGROUP BY institution\nORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC\n\n4. 获取未处理反馈\nSELECT * FROM paper_leads\nWHERE feedback_status = '未处理'\n\n5. 搜索关键词\nSELECT * FROM paper_leads\nWHERE keywords_matched @> ARRAY['mIF']","x":1430,"y":1850,"width":780,"height":750},
		
		{"id":"section6","type":"group","x":-50,"y":2850,"width":2300,"height":900,"label":"六、导出与通知层 (Export & Notification)"},
		{"id":"s6_csv","type":"text","text":"【CSV导出】CSVExporter\n\n字段（精简版）：\n- PMID\n- DOI\n- 文章标题\n- 发表时间\n- 通讯作者姓名\n- 通讯作者单位\n- 通讯作者邮箱\n- 等级\n- 分数\n- 来源链接\n\n导出规则：\n- 每日增量导出\n- 文件名：paper_leads_YYYY-MM-DD.csv\n- 编码：UTF-8-BOM (Excel兼容)\n- 位置：output/paper_leads/\n\n每周日全量导出：\n- 包含所有未归档线索\n- 标注变更状态：新增/已更新/无变化","x":-30,"y":2900,"width":700,"height":650},
		{"id":"s6_feishu","type":"text","text":"【飞书通知】FeishuNotifier\n\n消息类型：\n\n1. 每日摘要\n标题：📊 每日销售线索摘要\n内容：\n- 论文：X 篇\n- 处理：X 篇\n- 导出：X 条\n- 耗时：X 分钟\n\n2. 错误告警\n标题：⚠️ 系统异常\n内容：\n- 错误类型\n- 错误详情\n- 建议处理\n\n签名算法：\nstring_to_sign = timestamp + '\\n' + secret\nsign = Base64(HmacSHA256(string_to_sign, ''))\n\n配置：\n- FEISHU_WEBHOOK\n- FEISHU_SECRET","x":700,"y":2900,"width":700,"height":650},
		{"id":"s6_scheduler","type":"text","text":"【调度系统】Scheduler\n\n每日任务 (06:00):\n1. run_daily_task()\n   - 收集新 URL\n   - 去重\n   - 获取内容\n   - LLM 提取\n   - 评分入库\n   - 导出增量 CSV\n   - 发送飞书通知\n\n每周任务 (周日 06:00):\n2. run_full_export()\n   - 导出全量 CSV\n   - 标注变更状态\n   - 归档已处理线索\n\n配置：\n- SCHEDULE_HOUR=6\n- SCHEDULE_MINUTE=0\n\n异常处理：\n- 任务失败 → 发送错误通知\n- 重试机制 → 最多3次","x":1430,"y":2900,"width":780,"height":650},
		
		{"id":"section7","type":"group","x":-50,"y":3850,"width":2300,"height":700,"label":"七、完整工作流程 (Complete Workflow)"},
		{"id":"s7_flow","type":"text","text":"【端到端执行流程】\n\n1️⃣ 数据收集 (MultiModeCollector)\n   ├─ Search: Jina Search API 搜索关键词\n   ├─ Library: 翻页读取论文库\n   └─ 合并返回 URL 列表\n\n2️⃣ URL去重 (URLDeduplicator)\n   ├─ 提取 PMID/DOI\n   ├─ URL 标准化\n   └─ 返回唯一 URL\n\n3️⃣ 内容获取 (ContentFetcher)\n   ├─ 优先：Jina Reader API\n   ├─ 失败：Playwright 兜底\n   └─ 返回 Markdown 内容\n\n4️⃣ LLM提取 (LLMExtractor + RateLimiter)\n   ├─ 速率控制：30秒/请求\n   ├─ GLM-5 提取字段\n   ├─ JSON 解析\n   └─ 返回结构化数据\n\n5️⃣ 评分入库 (PaperScorer + Database)\n   ├─ 计算7维度分数\n   ├─ 映射等级 A/B/C/D\n   ├─ 检查重复 URL\n   └─ INSERT 到数据库\n\n6️⃣ 导出通知 (CSVExporter + FeishuNotifier)\n   ├─ 导出增量 CSV\n   ├─ 发送飞书摘要\n   └─ 记录执行日志","x":-30,"y":3900,"width":2000,"height":550},
		
		{"id":"section8","type":"group","x":-50,"y":"4650","width":2300,"height":900,"label":"八、配置与部署 (Configuration & Deployment)"},
		{"id":"s8_env","type":"text","text":"【环境变量 (.env)】\n\n# 数据库\nDATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://localhost/sleads_dev\n\n# API Keys\nJINA_API_KEY=jina_xxx\nZAI_API_KEY=xxx.tWSSQ0tmAAxUPSpT\nZAI_MODEL=glm-5\n\n# 飞书通知\nFEISHU_WEBHOOK=https://open.feishu.cn/...\nFEISHU_SECRET=VPZrSzhsvsU2vg4ZGDor9e\nTENDER_KEYWORDS=免疫荧光,mIF,病理诊断\n\n# 调度\nSCHEDULE_HOUR=6\nSCHEDULE_MINUTE=0\n\n# 日志\nLOG_LEVEL=INFO\nLOG_RETENTION_DAYS=30","x":-30,"y":4700,"width":650,"height":650},
		{"id":"s8_yaml","type":"text","text":"【YAML 配置文件】\n\nconfig/keywords.yaml\n- 搜索关键词（英文/中文）\n- 关联设备关键词\n- 招标关键词\n\nconfig/sources.yaml\n- 数据源 URL\n- 优先级设置\n- 速率限制\n\nconfig/scoring_paper.yaml\n- 论文评分权重\n- 等级区间\n- 关键词匹配规则\n\nconfig/scoring_tender.yaml\n- 招标评分权重\n- 等级区间\n- 预算匹配规则\n\nconfig/scheduler.yaml\n- 定时任务配置\n- 重试策略","x":650,"y":4700,"width":650,"height":650},
		{"id":"s8_loader","type":"text","text":"【ConfigLoader 实现】\n\nclass Config:\n    def __init__(self):\n        load_dotenv(override=True)\n    \n    @property\n    def database_url(self):\n        return os.getenv('DATABASE_URL')\n    \n    @property\n    def feishu_webhook(self):\n        return os.getenv('FEISHU_WEBHOOK')\n    \n    @property\n    def scoring_paper(self):\n        return load_yaml('scoring_paper.yaml')\n    \n    @property\n    def tender_keywords(self):\n        env = os.getenv('TENDER_KEYWORDS')\n        if env:\n            return [k.strip() for k in env.split(',')]\n        return self.keywords.get('tender', [])\n\n# 全局单例\nconfig = Config()\n\n特性：\n- override=True 强制使用 .env\n- 自动加载 YAML\n- 类型转换\n- 默认值回退","x":1330,"y":4700,"width":880,"height":650},
		
		{"id":"section9","type":"group","x":-50,"y":5650,"width":2300,"height":700,"label":"九、监控与维护 (Monitoring & Maintenance)"},
		{"id":"s9_log","type":"text","text":"【日志系统】\n\n日志级别：\n- INFO: 正常流程\n- WARNING: 可恢复错误\n- ERROR: 严重错误\n- DEBUG: 调试信息\n\n日志内容：\n- [时间戳] [级别] [模块] 消息\n- HTTP 请求记录\n- LLM API 调用\n- 数据库操作\n- 错误堆栈\n\n日志轮转：\n- 保留30天\n- 自动清理旧日志\n- 压缩归档\n\n文件位置：\nlogs/sleads_YYYY-MM-DD.log","x":-30,"y":5700,"width":750,"height":500},
		{"id":"s9_stats","type":"text","text":"【统计指标】\n\n实时统计：\n- 今日收集 URL 数\n- 今日处理论文数\n- LLM API 调用次数\n- 成功率\n- 平均处理时间\n\nContentFetcher 统计：\n- total_requests: 总请求数\n- jina_success: Jina 成功数\n- playwright_success: Playwright 成功数\n- success_rate: 成功率\n\nRateLimiter 统计：\n- total_requests: 总请求数\n- rate_limit_waits: 等待次数\n- retry_429: 429 重试次数","x":750,"y":5700,"width":750,"height":500},
		{"id":"s9_error","type":"text","text":"【异常处理】\n\n网络错误：\n- 超时：重试1次\n- 连接失败：记录日志\n- DNS 解析失败：跳过\n\nAPI 错误：\n- 429: 等待 Retry-After\n- 500: 重试最多3次\n- 401: 检查 API Key\n\n数据库错误：\n- IntegrityError: 重复键，跳过\n- ConnectionError: 重连\n- Timeout: 重试\n\nLLM 错误：\n- JSON 解析失败：记录内容\n- 字段缺失：警告，继续\n- 超时：重试\n\n通知：\n- 飞书发送失败：记录日志\n- 签名校验失败：检查密钥","x":1530,"y":5700,"width":700,"height":500}
	],
